<item>
            <title>[WICKET-2264] Ajax xml response is not validated correct</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-2264</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Ajax xml response is not validated correct&lt;br/&gt;
Try my quickstart project with Firefox. Clicking on the submit button should update the label above. But does not. See the result in the error log in firefox. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The control characters is not properly escaped. Ex: &quot;\u0014&quot; is written &lt;br/&gt;
as 0014 in the xml Ajax Response but should be . &apos;&amp;amp;#0014&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
See: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml/#dt-charref&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml/#dt-charref&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
